
📄 SIP Calculator  


 – Simple Documentation

🔷 Project Name:
SIP (Systematic Investment Plan) Calculator

🔷 Description:
Yeh ek simple web-based calculator hai jo users ko batata hai ki agar wo har mahine ek fix amount invest karein, to kitna paisa banega future mein. Isme user sliders se amount, return rate aur time select karta hai, aur result turant milta hai.

🏗️ Technologies Used:

    * HTML – Structure banane ke liye
    
    * CSS – Styling aur design ke liye
     
    * Bootstrap – Responsive layout ke liye
    
    * JavaScript – Calculation aur chart dikhane ke liye
    
    * Chart.js – Doughnut chart banane ke liye

📋 Features:

    3 sliders:

    *  Monthly Investment
    
    *  Expected Return Rate
     
    *  Time Period (Years)
     
    *  Real-time calculation jaise hi slider change karo
      
    *  Invested amount, Estimated returns, aur Total value dikhta hai
      
    *  Doughnut chart dikhata hai investment aur returns ka breakdown
      
    *  Responsive design – mobile/laptop dono pe achha dikhta hai
     
    *  Side section mein popular calculators ke links aur info card bhi hai

👩‍💻 User Flow:

User apna monthly investment set karta hai

Expected return rate aur time period choose karta hai

Niche result automatically update hota hai

Chart se easily samajh aata hai ki kitna paisa banega

📦 Folder Structure (Basic Idea):

    *   index.html – Main file
       
    *   css/style.css – Styling
       
    *   js/script.js – Logic and calculations
       
    *   Assets – Images and logos (optional)

✅ Conclusion:

Ye SIP Calculator ek useful tool hai jisse users apni mutual fund SIP planning easily kar sakte hain. Yeh tool real-time calculation aur easy UI ke saath bana hai taaki sab log use kar sakein bina kisi confusion ke.

